        {
            "title": "黃金能否重拾失去的動能?瑞銀集團發表看法",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FSohemaPO_oD8FNraAnbyA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_6_M_1440048362.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 黃金的急劇回調引發了市場對該金屬能否恢復上漲勢頭的疑問,但瑞銀集團的分析師表示,近期的疲軟可能只是暫時的。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行指出,黃金\"在1月份曾上漲高達25%\",但現在\"幾乎抹去了2026年的所有漲幅\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該金屬今年仍有上漲;然而,在過去一個月中已下跌近11%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管在地緣政治不確定性加劇的情況下,這種拋售似乎有悖常理,但瑞銀表示,這一走勢與歷史情況一致。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e38e72c7-de84-3f9c-9120-b29694528660-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"黃金並非總是在衝突期間上漲,尤其是在早期階段。經濟背景至關重要,\"該行寫道。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在這種情況下,能源價格上漲導致市場預期貨幣政策將收緊,從而增加了持有無收益資產的機會成本。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞銀強調,市場已發生劇烈變化,從預期\"2026年聯準會將降息兩次半,轉變為今年不會進一步寬鬆,甚至出現小幅加息的可能性\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">同樣,債券市場正在為歐洲央行和英國央行的多次加息定價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞銀認為這種反應過度,並指出能源價格上漲對經濟增長的潛在拖累。該行仍預期聯準會今年將放寬政策,並且隨著市場逃向流動性階段的消退,黃金需求將復甦。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"我們認為黃金的下跌可能相對短暫。雖然時機難以確定,但我們確實預期黃金將反彈,並預測這種貴金屬將在6月底前攀升至每盎司6,200美元,然後在2027年初回落至每盎司5,900美元,而目前約為每盎司4,500美元,\"瑞銀總結道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E8%83%BD%E5%90%A6%E9%87%8D%E6%8B%BE%E5%A4%B1%E5%8E%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%8B%95%E8%83%BD-%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95-172522367.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-01 02:00:27",
